Protocol and Ports
Keep default settings → Click Next
Scope
Under Remote IP address, select:
👉 These IP addresses
Click Add
Enter IP to block (Example: 1.2.3.4)
Click OK → Next
Action
Select Block the connection → Next
Profile
Select:
✔ Domain
✔ Private
✔ Public
Click Next
Name the rule
Example: Manual_Block_IP
Click Finish
